comments.body:
* How much do we want (want to ask) POs to participate in sprint planning / standups / wrapup? They may expect a more traditional meeting calendar (like "once a month" as opposed to "daily or twice a week whenever we're working on your product")
* What github is and how we use it.
  * Do we expect POs to have github accounts?
    * If so a list of POs and their github ids would be really helpful, perhaps along with a tech lead list.
* POs need to know some context about the cadance of our team's work cycles. They may not really know the difference between our team and EUS.
* Expectations for how communication happens, and reasons why.
